Edit team color styles
Published styles are shared with everyone on the team they can be used by all team members in any of their files Changing these styles will update them everywhere they re used Change these default colors to your team s colors by selecting a color layer and clicking on in the Design panel to the right 
Create color styles
To create new styles select a layer and fill it with the color you want as a style Then click on in the color styles menu 
Tip You can group styles together using the naming convention Group Color For example Fuschia 100
